trans-unit.source: Represents a design-time editor sheet for the properties of a <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression in the UI of a designer host at design time.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma folha de editor de tempo de design para as propriedades de um <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> expressão na interface de usuário de um host de designer em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor> class together with the RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet class to select the individual properties of a `RouteUrl` expression, and to combine the selected expression property values into a `RouteUrl` expression.
trans-unit.target: O designer visual usa o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor>classe junto com a classe RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet para selecionar as propriedades individuais de um `RouteUrl` expressão e combinar os valores de propriedade de expressão selecionada em um `RouteUrl` expressão.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method returns a RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet object.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName>método retorna um objeto RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: In the expressions dialog box, when you select a control property and bind it to a `RouteUrl` expression, the visual designer calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Na caixa de diálogo expressões, quando você seleciona uma propriedade de controle e associá-lo para um `RouteUrl` expressão, o visual designer chama o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>método.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the returned RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet object to prompt for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: O designer visual usa o objeto retornado de RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet para solicitar o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>Propriedades.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>

trans-unit.source: Once the properties are selected, the visual designer calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A> method to combine the properties into a `RouteUrl` expression string.
trans-unit.target: Depois que as propriedades são selecionadas, o visual designer chama o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A>método para combinar as propriedades em um `RouteUrl` cadeia de caracteres de expressão.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> property must be specified if the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> property is not specified.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>propriedade deve ser especificada se o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>propriedade não for especificada.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> property must be specified if the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> is not specified.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>propriedade deve ser especificada se o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>não for especificado.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Both properties may be specified.
trans-unit.target: Ambas as propriedades podem ser especificadas.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: The initial <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> property values are set using the input `expression` string.
trans-unit.target: Inicial <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A>valores de propriedade são definidos usando a entrada `expression` cadeia de caracteres.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.RouteUrlExpressionEditorSheet.RouteValues%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A> property is set using the input `serviceProvider` implementation.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A>propriedade é definida usando a entrada `serviceProvider` implementação.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression, used to initialize the expression editor sheet.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> expressão, usado para inicializar a folha de editor de expressão.

trans-unit.source: A service provider implementation supplied by the designer host, used to obtain additional design-time services.
trans-unit.target: Uma implementação de provedor de serviço fornecida pelo host do designer, usado para obter os serviços de tempo de design adicionais.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression that is formed by the expression editor sheet property values.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> expressão que é formado pelos valores de propriedade de folha de editor de expressão.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression string for the current settings in the sheet.
trans-unit.target: O <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> cadeia de caracteres de expressão para as configurações atuais na planilha.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression string is valid.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> cadeia de caracteres de expressão é válida.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""></xref> expression string is valid; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Se o <xref uid="langword_csharp_RouteUrl" name="RouteUrl" href=""> </xref> cadeia de caracteres de expressão for válido; caso contrário <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Os nomes de parâmetro de URL e valores que serão usados para gerar uma URL de uma rota.
